-- Queensland Rains Disrupting Coal Mines in Australia, Anglo American Says
-- B y   E l i s a b e t h   B e h r m a n n
-- 2010-10-11T04:04:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-11/queensland-rains-disrupting-coal-mines-in-australia-anglo-american-says.html
Heavy rain in Australia has hit some
of Anglo American Ltd.’s coal mining operations, Anglo said in
an e-mailed statement today.  The company has “experienced unusual rain at some of our
operations that is disrupting our ability to produce coal,”
according to the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
